Hold on... I need to be West of that boulder at (36, 15) to push it East into the fountain at (37, 15). So, can I move West to get there? Yes. (35, 14) is a fountain, and (35, 15) is floor. So I can move to (35,14) then South to (35, 15), then East to push that boulder in to the fountain!

So, the plan:

1.  Move West from (37, 13) to (36, 13).
